<node id="Diabetes">
  <data key="d0">Diabetes</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Diabetes is a chronic health condition that poses a significant public health challenge globally. It encompasses a group of diseases that affect how the body utilizes blood sugar (glucose), notably including both type 1 and type 2 diabetes mellitus. As a metabolic disorder, diabetes is characterized by prolonged high blood sugar levels, with type 2 diabetes often associated with metabolic syndrome.

This chronic condition requires careful management of blood sugar regulation, necessitating different strategies for type 1 and type 2 variants. The management of diabetes can involve lifestyle modifications, medical supervision, and consistent monitoring to mitigate the risk of associated complications. People with diabetes face increased susceptibility to a range of health threats, particularly related to the vascular system. Serious complications can arise from the condition, including neuropathy, retinopathy, and even the need for amputations.

In order to effectively address diabetes as a public health issue, there is a pressing need for data collection and the implementation of management strategies that promote healthy lifestyles. The overall impact of diabetes extends beyond individual health, affecting broader public health systems due to its prevalence and complication rates.&lt;SEP&gt;Diabetes is a chronic disease characterized by persistently high blood glucose levels and has three main types: type I, type II, and gestational diabetes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-55d2691a8c714949752d249721fec5e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5384df975133ef2a52113cd3ca0f897e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eb0252816f7fbee4c50f79ef3ee56063&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-85ef35aaa38ac4f0c032c8bc3f6df559&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-453e4228f98ddea76e07ce405d13fd32&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2173942c84747feba52cff952903a7f5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8e3bf51a75faa8eb6fe5fe7a0e509efe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7ef79f22f40772c2060b439008ce485b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8e236a5eba0e1dbf843d32e509da045&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a07cef05efd947a538701b4c41b162b1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5c3e866099ac4f8457930aab67cc3bd0</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1769582109</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
