<node id="Diabetic Neuropathy">
  <data key="d0">Diabetic Neuropathy</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Diabetic neuropathy is the most common microvascular complication of diabetes mellitus, leading to sensory and motor disorders.</data>
