  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Distal symmetrical sensory-motor polyneuropathy is a form of neuropathy that can be classified into early, symptomatic, and severe stages.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0748670b42b0f4e0b2ed9c5ce62d54e7</data>
