<node id="Chronic Complications of Diabetes">
  <data key="d0">Chronic Complications of Diabetes</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Chronic complications of diabetes refer to long-term health issues arising from the condition, including diabetic retinopathy and other serious complications.&lt;SEP&gt;Chronic complications of diabetes include various serious conditions like neuropathy, recurrent infections, and amputations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0748670b42b0f4e0b2ed9c5ce62d54e7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7ef79f22f40772c2060b439008ce485b</data>
