  <data key="d2">Screening strategies refer to recommended methods for detecting diabetic retinopathy in patients with diabetes.&lt;SEP&gt;Screening strategies are methods used to detect cardiovascular autonomic neuropathy and distal sensory-motor neuropathy in patients.</data>
