<node id="Eastern Mediterranean Region">
  <data key="d0">Eastern Mediterranean Region</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">The Eastern Mediterranean Region is a geographical area facing a rising incidence of diabetes mellitus and associated health challenges.&lt;SEP&gt;The Eastern Mediterranean Region is characterized by high rates of diabetes and significant public health challenges.&lt;SEP&gt;The Eastern Mediterranean Region encompasses various countries and is characterized by a diverse population and high diabetes prevalence.&lt;SEP&gt;The Eastern Mediterranean Region is highlighted as a location where screening for type 2 diabetes in children is recommended.&lt;SEP&gt;The Eastern Mediterranean Region is experiencing a rising prevalence of type 2 diabetes and related health issues.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5384df975133ef2a52113cd3ca0f897e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d8c827cc2249067692290d6a8a0e8018&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eb1bc7614fcd68decf9461b3b6290e95&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-12fe828372a20b6606e010f0fd5e6263&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f15f59b3ff05825a61f252ed8f9a74e1</data>
