<node id="IGT">
  <data key="d0">IGT</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">IGT (Impaired Glucose Tolerance) is a transient metabolic condition that indicates a higher risk of developing diabetes and is often assessed via an OGTT.</data>
