<node id="WHO">
  <data key="d0">WHO</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The World Health Organization (WHO) is the governing body that defined diabetes mellitus and sets guidelines for its prevention and management.&lt;SEP&gt;The WHO (World Health Organization) provides recommendations for diagnosing and managing metabolic conditions such as IGT and IFG.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-42a410eaaaed4b7428f5e95a4c7c4580&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-85ef35aaa38ac4f0c032c8bc3f6df559</data>
