<node id="Protein-Deficient Pancreatic Diabetes">
  <data key="d0">Protein-Deficient Pancreatic Diabetes</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Protein-deficient pancreatic diabetes is considered a malnutrition-modulated form of diabetes mellitus that may need further studies.</data>
