<node id="Fibrocalculous Pancreatic Diabetes">
  <data key="d0">Fibrocalculous Pancreatic Diabetes</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Fibrocalculous pancreatic diabetes is now classified as fibrocalculous pancreatopathy, which may lead to diabetes mellitus.</data>
