  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The WHO Regional Office for the Eastern Mediterranean is the branch of the World Health Organization responsible for public health initiatives in the Eastern Mediterranean region.&lt;SEP&gt;The WHO Regional Office for the Eastern Mediterranean is involved in diabetes prevention and control efforts in the region.</data>
