<node id="United Arab Emirates">
  <data key="d0">United Arab Emirates</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">The United Arab Emirates has a diabetes prevalence rate as high as 20% and is part of the Eastern Mediterranean Region with significant health challenges.&lt;SEP&gt;The United Arab Emirates is one of the Eastern Mediterranean countries reporting high diabetes prevalence rates.&lt;SEP&gt;United Arab Emirates is where a study on glucose intolerance and associated factors was conducted.</data>
