  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Triglycerides are a type of fat found in the blood, with high levels being a criterion for metabolic syndrome diagnosis.&lt;SEP&gt;Triglycerides are a type of fat found in the blood, with specific targets set for management in diabetic patients.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8361af576f7e73b0bd2ea813976f60b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e8e236a5eba0e1dbf843d32e509da045</data>
