  <data key="d0">Statins</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Statins are a class of drugs used to lower LDL cholesterol and triglycerides while raising HDL cholesterol levels for cardiovascular disease management.&lt;SEP&gt;Statins are a class of medications used as first-line therapy for patients with high cholesterol and are noted for their effectiveness in lowering LDL cholesterol.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8361af576f7e73b0bd2ea813976f60b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-21112bd6ed1fe7896dbf55a52bc45a2d</data>
