  <data key="d0">Cairo</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Cairo is the capital city of Egypt, hosting the Regional Office for the Eastern Mediterranean branch of the WHO.&lt;SEP&gt;Cairo is the capital of Egypt, hosting several significant health consultations by the World Health Organization.&lt;SEP&gt;Cairo is a city in Egypt referenced in relation to regional consultations and meetings on diabetes.</data>
