  <data key="d0">UK Prospective Diabetes Study Group</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The UK Prospective Diabetes Study Group conducted research on blood pressure association with diabetes-related retinopathy incidence and progression.&lt;SEP&gt;The UK Prospective Diabetes Study Group is a research group focused on studying diabetes and its management in the UK.&lt;SEP&gt;The UK Prospective Diabetes Study Group is a research group associated with an important study on diabetes complications.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-57782c3301473bc8e8dafd9683ab2650&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942e000d0de99e8628ab9c8bcbe83419&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7ef79f22f40772c2060b439008ce485b</data>
