<node id="WHO Technical Report Series">
  <data key="d0">WHO Technical Report Series</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The WHO Technical Report Series provides recommendations and guidelines on various health issues, including diabetes mellitus prevention.</data>
