<node id="UKPDS 38">
  <data key="d0">UKPDS 38</data>
  <data key="d1">study</data>
  <data key="d2">UKPDS 38 refers to a study that examines tight blood pressure control and its effects on complications in type 2 diabetes.&lt;SEP&gt;The UKPDS 38 is an important study that examined the impact of blood pressure control on complications related to type 2 diabetes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-57782c3301473bc8e8dafd9683ab2650&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-942e000d0de99e8628ab9c8bcbe83419</data>
