  <data key="d0">UKPDS 33</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">UKPDS 33 refers to a study comparing intensive blood glucose control using sulphonylureas or insulin versus conventional treatment in patients with type 2 diabetes.</data>
