  <data key="d0">Thiazide Diuretics</data>
  <data key="d1">drug</data>
  <data key="d2">Thiazide diuretics are medications recommended as initial therapy options for managing hypertension in patients with diabetes.&lt;SEP&gt;Thiazide Diuretics are a type of diuretic medication typically used for hypertension control but may not be preferred in cases of fluid retention.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-453e4228f98ddea76e07ce405d13fd32&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fd4cfbed43aa26af0eef694fecac2177</data>
