<node id="Ophthalmoscopy Skills">
  <data key="d0">Ophthalmoscopy Skills</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Ophthalmoscopy skills refer to the abilities required by primary care physicians to properly examine the retina and detect conditions like retinopathy.</data>
