<node id="Three Waves of Development">
  <data key="d0">Three Waves of Development</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The three waves of development in deep learning include early models in the 1940s-1960s, connectionist approaches in the 1980s-1990s, and the current resurgence starting in 2006.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7030ceb5e481db7469c5a663054ab0ff</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1769578866</data>
