<node id="Cybernetics">
  <data key="d0">Cybernetics</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Cybernetics refers to the field of study that began in the 1940s–1960s, focused on biological learning theories and the development of neural networks.&lt;SEP&gt;Cybernetics is an interdisciplinary field that studies the structure of regulatory systems, playing a significant role in the early development of artificial intelligence models.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7030ceb5e481db7469c5a663054ab0ff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5f255acea8c3a7b10af84028b23d7ead</data>
