<node id="Eigenvalues">
  <data key="d0">Eigenvalues</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Eigenvalues are scalars associated with a square matrix that scale eigenvectors when multiplied by the matrix.&lt;SEP&gt;Eigenvalues are scalars associated with a matrix that provide important information about its characteristics, particularly in terms of transformation and scaling effects.&lt;SEP&gt;Eigenvalues are scalar values that provide important information about a matrix regarding its properties and transformations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f81436ceefbaa6d5dc02610dd8127f9b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d0d3be7ce3dfb930212c12aac0c54ff0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-443f6360d2d3fc61bef3f5a8c109e2f2</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
