  <data key="d0">Positive Semidefinite Matrix</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">A positive semidefinite matrix has all eigenvalues that are non-negative, indicating certain constraints in optimization scenarios.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f81436ceefbaa6d5dc02610dd8127f9b</data>
