  <data key="d0">Singular Value Decomposition (SVD)</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Singular Value Decomposition is a method for factorizing a matrix, useful for extracting information analogous to eigendecomposition but applicable to any real matrix.</data>
