<node id="Orthogonal Matrix">
  <data key="d0">Orthogonal Matrix</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">An orthogonal matrix is a square matrix whose rows and columns are orthogonal unit vectors, preserving angles and lengths during transformations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f81436ceefbaa6d5dc02610dd8127f9b</data>
