  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Neural networks are computational models inspired by the human brain, used in various artificial intelligence applications.&lt;SEP&gt;Neural networks are computational models inspired by the human brain that have seen increased success due to advancements in computational resources and model size over time.&lt;SEP&gt;Neural Networks are computational models inspired by human brain structure, capable of learning complex tasks like image recognition and sequence prediction.</data>
