  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Linear regression is a supervised learning algorithm that fits a straight line over the data to predict outcomes.&lt;SEP&gt;Linear regression is a method used to model the relationship between a dependent variable and one or more independent variables by fitting a linear equation.</data>
