  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">LASSO (Least Absolute Shrinkage and Selection Operator) is a technique used to reduce overfitting by eliminating less predictive features from the model.&lt;SEP&gt;LASSO is a regression analysis method that performs both variable selection and regularization to enhance prediction accuracy and interpretability.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-766aef888d040609f74bd8aa547e4350&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-189a42780d202026d1c3290c001f80ee</data>
