  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Support Vector Machine (SVM) is a supervised learning technique that finds the optimal decision boundary for classification tasks.&lt;SEP&gt;Support Vector Machine is a supervised learning algorithm used for classification and regression that finds the hyperplane that best separates the classes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-766aef888d040609f74bd8aa547e4350&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-189a42780d202026d1c3290c001f80ee</data>
