  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">A Confusion Matrix is a tool used to summarize the performance of a classification algorithm, detailing true and false predictions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-af13cdaacfcf632c4d70cffbf33bfb60</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
