  <data key="d0">Area Under the Curve (AUC)</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Area Under the Curve (AUC) quantifies the overall performance of a binary classification model, summarizing the ROC curve.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-af13cdaacfcf632c4d70cffbf33bfb60</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1769582339</data>
