<edge source="Eigenvalues" target="Eigenvectors">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Eigenvalues correspond to eigenvectors, indicating how the scale of the eigenvector changes when multiplied by a matrix.&lt;SEP&gt;Eigenvalues and eigenvectors reveal key properties of a matrix during linear transformations.</data>
